  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tower Knight is a deck-building & tower defense strategy game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939570/extras/1a751edb3cd275924142ae3478910f03.poster.avif?t=1727111229\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939570/extras/1a751edb3cd275924142ae3478910f03.webm?t=1727111229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939570/extras/1a751edb3cd275924142ae3478910f03.mp4?t=1727111229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Make different plans for each challenge's starting deck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build your deck and adapt your strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The map grows as you play your cards.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939570/extras/79b5e1a848e559af73eb3c368ed3c471.poster.avif?t=1727111229\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939570/extras/79b5e1a848e559af73eb3c368ed3c471.webm?t=1727111229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939570/extras/79b5e1a848e559af73eb3c368ed3c471.mp4?t=1727111229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Victory and Defeat</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Win by surrounding all enemy towers with walls.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Your knight can defend themselves, but has limited health.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Deck-Building & Tower Defense</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build your deck and balance between attack, resource, and buff cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Survive by playing the cards drawn from your deck using energy and gold.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In game music and trailer music is courtesy of PGN Music.</p>",
