imited health.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Deck-Building & Tower Defense</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build your deck and balance between attack, resource, and buff cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Survive by playing the cards drawn from your deck using energy and gold.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In game music and trailer music is courtesy of PGN Music.</p>",
